{"type":"message","id":"14db09a4","parentId":"a065d07d","timestamp":"2026-04-15T04:54:14.632Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 补一条刚跑完的异步检查结果，和刚才判断一致：\n\n- `using-superpowers` 技能文件其实是**存在的**\n  - 找到路径：`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/using-superpowers/SKILL.md`\n- 之前报错那个路径是错的，指到了：\n  - `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/skills/using-superpowers/SKILL.md`\n- 另外我也确认了 OpenClaw 本体代码里确实有面板相关实现和控制 UI 配置写入逻辑，不是我误判。\n\n所以现在结论更稳了：\n\n1. 之前那个技能报错，不是核心故障，只是**读错路径**\n2. 你这个“修改配置文件后面板自动关闭”，核心还是**面板代理层自动回写配置，触发 Gateway 重载**\n\n如果你同意，我下一步就直接把这个自动写配置逻辑打补丁禁掉。  \n回我一句 **继续修** 就行。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ca9828e1b466e440169df19eebd448196b622a9d737823ffa\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":44464,"output":255,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44719,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776228843982,"responseId":"resp_0ca9828e1b466e440169df19eda5ec81968b90e29bf645d232"}}
